                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Setting up Virtual Environments"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "To start with project, it would be better to have a virtual environment. Virtual environment can help us to create an isolated or separate environment. This will help us to avoid conflicts in dependencies across projects. If you write pip freeze on your terminal you will see all the installed packages on your computer. If we use virtualenv, we will access only packages which are specific for that project. Open your terminal and install virtualenv"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "asabeneh@Asabeneh:~$ pip install virtualenv"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Inside the 30DaysOfPython folder create a flask_project folder."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "After installing the virtualenv package go to your project folder and create a virtual env by writing:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "For Mac/Linux:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project\\$ virtualenv venv"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "For Windows:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "C:\\Users\\User\\Documents\\30DaysOfPython\\flask_project>python -m venv venv"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "I prefer to call the new project venv, but feel free to name it differently. Let us check if the the venv was created by using ls (or dir for windows command prompt) command."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project$ ls\nvenv/"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Let us activate the virtual environment by writing the following command at our project folder."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "For Mac/Linux:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project$ source venv/bin/activate"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Activation of the virtual environment in Windows may very on Windows Power shell and git bash."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "For Windows Power Shell:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "C:\\Users\\User\\Documents\\30DaysOfPython\\flask_project> venv\\Scripts\\activate"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "For Windows Git bash:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "C:\\Users\\User\\Documents\\30DaysOfPython\\flask_project> venv\\Scripts\\. activate"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "After you write the activation command, your project directory will start with venv. See the example below."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "(venv) asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project$"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Now, lets check the available packages in this project by writing pip freeze. You will not see any packages."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "We are going to do a small flask project so let us install flask package to this project."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "(venv) asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project$ pip install Flask"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "Now, let us write pip freeze to see a list of installed packages in the project:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "(venv) asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython/flask_project$ pip freeze\nClick==7.0\nFlask==1.1.1\nitsdangerous==1.1.0\nJinja2==2.10.3\nMarkupSafe==1.1.1\nWerkzeug==0.16.0"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "When you finish you should dactivate active project using"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "em",
                        "attributes": {},
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "deactivate"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "pre",
                "attributes": {
                    "className": [
                        "codehilite"
                    ]
                },
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Element",
                        "tagName": "code",
                        "attributes": {
                            "className": [
                                "language-sh"
                            ]
                        },
                        "children": [
                            {
                                "type": "Text",
                                "content": "(venv) asabeneh@Asabeneh:~/Desktop/30DaysOfPython$ deactivate"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "Element",
                "tagName": "p",
                "attributes": {},
                "children": [
                    {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "content": "The necessary modules to work with flask are installed. Now, your project directory is ready for a flask project. You should include the venv to your .gitignore file not to push it to github."
                    }
                ]
            },
